10. What is the value of x in the below snippet?
reg [2:0] a, b;
reg [2:0]x;
initial
begin
a=3'd5;
b=3’b111;
x= a | b;
end
SOLUTION: x = 3'111

11. What is the value of x in the below snippet?
reg [2:0]a;
reg [2:0]x;
initial
begin
a = 3'd4;
x = ^a;
end 
SOLUTION: 3'001  [4=100,,1^0^0= 1]

