a = 4'd10;
X= (a>>1);
end
SOLUTION: binary value of 10= 1010,
          a=1010,, a>>1 i.e 0101
          now value of x is 2'b01

13. Find the value of b in the below snippet.
reg [3:0]a;
reg [6:0]b;
